847
00:51:41,200 --> 00:51:44,610
People might think she's bad luck.

848
00:51:44,620 --> 00:51:47,150
But that's nonsense!

849
00:51:47,160 --> 00:51:49,320
We're married.

850
00:51:49,330 --> 00:51:51,220
She must be miserable.

851
00:51:51,230 --> 00:51:53,090
Don't tell your father,

852
00:51:53,100 --> 00:51:55,350
