853
00:52:03,520 --> 00:52:04,880
Hello, mother.

854
00:52:04,890 --> 00:52:06,510
Would you like some tea?

855
00:52:06,520 --> 00:52:10,090
I want to make the exchange first.

856
00:52:10,100 --> 00:52:11,280
Okay.

857
00:52:16,790 --> 00:52:18,940
Give them to me first.

858
00:52:18,960 --> 00:52:20,850
You really won't tell them?

859
00:52:20,850 --> 00:52:22,580
I won't.

860
00:52:22,600 --> 00:52:26,120
This is our little secret, okay?

861
00:52:26,120 --> 00:52:27,920
Of course.

862
00:52:28,520 --> 00:52:30,010
Then give that to me first.

863
00:52:30,020 --> 00:52:31,840
You have to give me those first.

864
00:52:31,850 --> 00:52:33,420
I have the envelope here.

865
00:52:33,430 --> 00:52:35,510
So you should take them out.

866
00:52:43,460 --> 00:52:44,990
Open them.

867
00:52:45,000 --> 00:52:46,350
Why?

868
00:52:46,350 --> 00:52:49,880
Please open them. I must check.

869
00:52:49,890 --> 00:52:52,780
Then show me the envelope.

870
00:53:04,430 --> 00:53:06,420
You can't do this!

871
00:53:09,730 --> 00:53:11,520
You're pretty smart.

872
00:53:11,960 --> 00:53:15,790
I went to college. I can't give you this.

873
00:53:15,790 --> 00:53:18,440
You are just like me.

874
00:53:18,460 --> 00:53:22,890
If we open a tea room, it'd be a success.

875
00:53:30,250 --> 00:53:32,010
Happy?

876
00:53:32,020 --> 00:53:33,010
Give it to me.

877
00:53:33,020 --> 00:53:35,050
Let's exchange them at the same time.

878
00:53:40,460 --> 00:53:43,220
Let go on the count of three.

879
00:53:44,060 --> 00:53:47,690
One, two!

880
00:53:50,930 --> 00:53:53,510
You're pretty tough.

881
00:53:53,520 --> 00:53:56,420
How did you know I'd grab at two?

882
00:53:56,930 --> 00:53:59,990
I went to college, and I was a teacher.

883
00:54:06,120 --> 00:54:07,420
What's this?

884
00:54:07,430 --> 00:54:09,320
How could you do this?

885
00:54:09,330 --> 00:54:11,240
You tricked me?

886
00:54:11,250 --> 00:54:14,090
I only got back what you stole.

887
00:54:14,100 --> 00:54:17,050
I have no reason to give you money.

888
00:54:20,500 --> 00:54:22,920
I'm your mother in law!

889
00:54:22,930 --> 00:54:25,420
What kind of daughter in law does this?

890
00:54:25,430 --> 00:54:28,490
What about what you did to me?

891
00:54:28,500 --> 00:54:31,120
I did everything I could for you.

892
00:54:31,120 --> 00:54:33,840
I gave you $10,000 behind Sangnam's back.

893
00:54:33,850 --> 00:54:36,580
You hurt him when he was little,

894
00:54:36,600 --> 00:54:39,850
but I was happy about you and him.

895
00:54:39,850 --> 00:54:43,480
I didn't care if he got mad at me.

896
00:54:43,500 --> 00:54:46,490
But you stole father's key

897
00:54:46,500 --> 00:54:48,850
and turned Sangnam against me.

898
00:54:48,850 --> 00:54:50,880
I won't let this go on.

899
00:54:51,830 --> 00:54:54,050
You won't? How dare you?

900
00:54:54,060 --> 00:54:56,320
I won't just sit here and...

901
00:54:58,120 --> 00:55:00,540
Sangnam. Sangnam.

902
00:55:00,560 --> 00:55:01,890
Sangnam, listen to me.

903
00:55:01,890 --> 00:55:03,280
She's framing me!

904
00:55:03,290 --> 00:55:05,010
Sangnam, listen to me!

905
00:55:05,600 --> 00:55:07,620
