- I said get out!

907
00:55:11,120 --> 00:55:15,280
I'm embarrassed of thinking of you as my mom.

908
00:55:15,290 --> 00:55:17,650
And I regret meeting you again.

909
00:55:17,660 --> 00:55:21,220
I'm devastated you're my birth mother,

910
00:55:21,230 --> 00:55:24,820
