911
00:55:24,830 --> 00:55:27,490
I can't believe I thought of you as my mom.

912
00:55:27,500 --> 00:55:29,920
You don't deserve the title.

913
00:55:29,930 --> 00:55:31,090
Sangnam.

914
00:55:31,100 --> 00:55:33,740
Please leave.

915
00:55:33,750 --> 00:55:35,740
Don't say anything.

916
00:55:37,200 --> 00:55:38,590
Leave.

917
00:55:39,160 --> 00:55:41,490
Sangnam! Sangnam!

918
00:55:41,500 --> 00:55:45,520
Sangnam! Sangnam! Oh, Sangnam...

919
00:55:45,520 --> 00:55:47,510
Sangnam.

920
00:56:00,790 --> 00:56:04,320
I'm sorry things turned out this way.

921
00:56:04,330 --> 00:56:07,950
I didn't want anyone else to find out.

922
00:56:07,960 --> 00:56:10,890
After some time passes and

923
00:56:10,890 --> 00:56:14,310
Sangnam can  take you back again,

924
00:56:14,330 --> 00:56:16,740
I'll call you.

925
00:56:16,750 --> 00:56:19,550
Goodbye.

926
00:56:50,460 --> 00:56:53,020
Why did you come?

927
00:56:53,020 --> 00:56:55,880
I could've taken care of it.

928
00:56:57,330 --> 00:56:59,320
I'm sorry.

929
00:57:00,960 --> 00:57:03,050
I'm really sorry.

930
00:57:05,020 --> 00:57:08,150
I don't even know where to begin.

931
