935
00:57:26,230 --> 00:57:29,790
Why didn't you tell me about your parents?

936
00:57:32,390 --> 00:57:34,190
Why didn't you tell me?

937
00:57:34,200 --> 00:57:35,990
We're married.

938
00:57:37,730 --> 00:57:40,450
Did aunt tell you?

939
00:57:40,460 --> 00:57:41,820
Yes.

940
00:57:41,830 --> 00:57:44,490
How could you keep that a secret?

941
00:57:52,460 --> 00:57:55,030
Why did you suffer alone? You fool.

942
00:58:00,660 --> 00:58:02,690
